---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Excavating Lawrenceburg Indiana | Professional Excavation Services | Probst Excavating"
  description="Top-rated excavating services in Lawrenceburg, Indiana. Family-owned excavation company with 20+ years experience. Licensed, bonded & insured. Residential & commercial excavation, land clearing, sewer lines. Free estimates."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
      Excavating Services in Lawrenceburg, Indiana
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        When you need professional <strong>excavating in Lawrenceburg, Indiana</strong>, Probst Excavating Services 
        delivers the quality and reliability you deserve. For over 20 years, we've been the trusted choice for 
        residential and commercial excavation throughout Lawrenceburg, Dearborn County, and the Tri-State area.
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Choose Probst for Lawrenceburg Excavating?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">✓ Local Lawrenceburg Expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We know Lawrenceburg's terrain, soil conditions, and local regulations inside and out.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">✓ 20+ Years Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Two decades of successful excavation projects throughout Dearborn County.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">✓ Licensed & Insured</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Fully bonded and insured for your complete protection and peace of mind.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">✓ Owner On-Site</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Family-owned business where the owner is present on every job.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Comprehensive Excavating Services in Lawrenceburg, IN</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Residential Excavation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
              Expert excavating for new home construction, additions, and remodeling projects throughout Lawrenceburg.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Foundation excavation and preparation</li>
              <li>Basement excavation</li>
              <li>Driveway and walkway excavation</li>
              <li>Pool excavation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Commercial Excavation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
              Large-scale excavating for commercial developments, parking lots, and business properties in Lawrenceburg.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Site development and preparation</li>
              <li>Parking lot excavation</li>
              <li>Building foundation excavation</li>
              <li>Utility trenching</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Land Clearing & Site Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
              Professional land clearing for new construction and development projects in Lawrenceburg, Indiana.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Tree and brush removal</li>
              <li>Stump grinding and removal</li>
              <li>Lot clearing for new builds</li>
              <li>Grading and leveling</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sewer Line Services</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
              Advanced trenchless sewer line repair and replacement for Lawrenceburg homes and businesses.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Sewer line excavation and repair</li>
              <li>Trenchless sewer replacement</li>
              <li>Sewer line inspection</li>
              <li>Emergency sewer services</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Drainage Solutions</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
              Storm drainage and water management excavation for Lawrenceburg properties.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>Storm drainage installation</li>
              <li>French drain systems</li>
              <li>Catch basin installation</li>
              <li>Grading for proper drainage</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Excavating in Lawrenceburg: Local Knowledge Matters</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Lawrenceburg, Indiana presents unique challenges for excavation work. From the Ohio River valley terrain 
          to varying soil compositions throughout Dearborn County, local expertise is essential for successful excavation projects.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Our team understands Lawrenceburg's specific conditions:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Soil Composition:</strong> We're experienced with the clay-heavy and varied soil types common in Lawrenceburg</li>
          <li><strong>Water Tables:</strong> Knowledge of seasonal water levels and drainage patterns</li>
          <li><strong>Local Regulations:</strong> Familiarity with Dearborn County and City of Lawrenceburg permitting</li>
          <li><strong>Terrain Challenges:</strong> Experience working with sloped properties and hillside excavation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Serving All of Lawrenceburg, Indiana</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Probst Excavating proudly serves all neighborhoods and areas throughout Lawrenceburg, including:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-gray-700">
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Downtown Lawrenceburg</li>
            <li>Greendale</li>
            <li>West Harrison</li>
            <li>Hidden Valley</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Tanner's Creek area</li>
            <li>State Route 50 corridor</li>
            <li>US Highway 50 area</li>
            <li>All surrounding rural areas</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Excavating Process in Lawrenceburg</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Free On-Site Estimate</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">We visit your Lawrenceburg property to assess the project and provide a detailed quote.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Planning & Permits</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">We handle all necessary permits and coordinate with local Lawrenceburg authorities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Professional Excavation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Our experienced team completes your excavation with precision and efficiency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Site Cleanup & Final Grading</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">We leave your property clean and properly graded for the next construction phase.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready for Professional Excavating in Lawrenceburg?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Contact Probst Excavating today for your free estimate. We're Lawrenceburg's trusted excavation experts 
          with over 20 years of local experience.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/contact" 
            class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
          >
            Get Your Free Estimate
          </a>
          <a 
            href="https://www.facebook.com/probstexcavating/" 
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-block bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-800 transition border-2 border-white"
          >
            Message Us on Facebook
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions - Excavating in Lawrenceburg, IN</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How much does excavating cost in Lawrenceburg, Indiana?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Excavation costs vary based on project size, soil conditions, and scope of work. We provide free, 
              detailed estimates for all Lawrenceburg excavation projects. Contact us for an accurate quote.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do I need permits for excavation in Lawrenceburg?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Most excavation projects require permits from the City of Lawrenceburg or Dearborn County. 
              We're familiar with local requirements and can assist with the permitting process.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How long does a typical excavation project take?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Timeline varies by project. Residential foundation excavation typically takes 1-3 days, while larger 
              commercial projects may take longer. We provide accurate timelines during the estimate process.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Are you licensed and insured in Lawrenceburg?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Yes! Probst Excavating is fully licensed, bonded, and insured. We carry comprehensive liability 
              and workers' compensation insurance for your protection.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white mt-16 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        © {new Date().getFullYear()} Probst Excavating Services. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">
        Professional Excavating in Lawrenceburg, Indiana | Licensed, Bonded & Insured
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
